{"tid":2275112,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"社會大學 fresher 圍爐區","createTime":"2020-11-07T02:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T05:37:15.000Z","uid":373525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb98766c9fdf4dcd7e96d625baad1ae4ed2b76a0","tid":2275112,"uid":373525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"歡迎唔同嘅Fg 入泥交流下心路歷程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翻左就一個月工，覺得生活對比學生時期已經好大變化。<br />\n<br />\n依家七點就醒，放工翻到屋企都八點幾，食個飯冲完涼都九點幾，hea一陣十點幾就訓，每一日都係咁，有規律到自己都嚇親自己。<br />\n<br />\n如果係星期五六都唔會夜過十二點訓，因為驚打亂生理時鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOffice 嘅同事其實都算nice ，條team都算後生，翻工時都會有講有笑。<br />\n<br />\n不過又feel到大家都有少少距離感，例如成班食飯好似冇乜野講，或者好多時都係各有各揾fd食。<br />\n<br />\n果種似熟但實際又唔熟嘅關係真係好尷尬，但又唔可以完完全舖放棄哂佢地唔去同佢地交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋真係好佩服啲人星期五放工仲可以玩到凌晨一兩點，我頂多同人食完飯九點幾已經攰到想翻去訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669d5d6eee845c8077e4168758e1bb134f19404a","tid":2275112,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"返咗個幾月仲係冇assign嘢畀我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己毒到同事都唔想理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42093de97fa104f05075167feb9636619ec5738b","tid":2275112,"uid":373525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"669d5d6eee845c8077e4168758e1bb134f19404a","tid":2275112,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"返咗個幾月仲係冇assign嘢畀我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己毒到同事都唔想理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"有冇試過同manager 講叫佢俾野你做<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm